title: Paradise 01 - 04 (2005 - 2010) cbr
description:
Maurania in a distant land of jungles, rain-soaked, King Rodon awaits the arrival of his daughter, whom he has not seen for ten years, while still a child. But the plane from Europe was shot down by the rebels. Miraculously survived the accident, but became amnesic, daughter of Rodon is gathered in the palace of the Prince of the City Mandargane. Her passport shows her name is Ann Smith, and she lives in Geneva.


enjoy
